"2:153:5" : {s: 2, a: 153, w: 5, r: "صبر", t: "بِٱلصَّبْرِ", l: "صَبْر", lc: 15, tl: "bil-ṣabri", lb: "ধৈর্য্য",e: "through patience", b: "সবরের সাথে", i: "dengan sabar", f: 4, rm: "to bind, be patient or constant, endure patiently, steadily adhere to reason and command, restrain from what reason and law forbid, restrain from manifesting grief, agitation and impatience. The word being the contrary of jaza (manifestation of grief and agitation)."},
